GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
New Delhi, the 22nd May, 1957.
The undersigned is directed to inform Members of the
Council of Ministers that Shri Alungal Mathai Thomas
assumed office as Deputy Minister with effect from the forenoon of
21st May, 1957. He will be attached to the Ministry of Food
and Agriculture.
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded to the Deputy Chairman, Planning Commission,
for information.
